            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Albertus">Aliperto</name></persName> filio
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Asifridus">Asfridi</name></persName>, havitator
                        in <placeName key="#Vici"><rs key="#Vici">vico</rs> Septiniana</placeName>,
                        quia ante os annos una cum filio meo <persName key="#Priests"><name
                                ref="Robertus">Rotperto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> a fundamentis in proprio nostro <rs
                            key="#Private_foundations">construximus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> in honorem Dei et <orgName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Churches #Private_foundations"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/617">Sancti Fridiani</orgName> in ipso loco. Ubi
                        et in ipsa sacrationis diem, in presentia viri beatissimi <persName
                            key="#Bishops" ref="#people/706">Andreati</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et de <rs key="#Priests">sacerdotibus</rs>
                        eius et cuncta congregatione populi, offeruerimus nosmetipsos cum omnibus
                        rebus nostris (…) in ipsa Dei ecclesia (…). Qui et ipse episcopus per
                        absolutionem domni viri beatissimi <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/343">Peredei</persName> in Dei nomine <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopi</rs>, cuius <rs key="#Dioecesis">diocese</rs> esse videtur,
                        ipsam ecclesiam sacravit. <foreign>Ora i due donano la stessa chiesa e i
                            loro beni</foreign> Deo et tibi <orgName key="#Mother_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68">beati Sancti Martini</orgName>, ubi est
                        domus episcoporum, in <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Mother_churches" ref="#places/4"
                            >Lucense</placeName>. <foreign>Si riservano vita natural durante
                            di</foreign> in <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs> ipsius
                        ecclesiae habitando, regendo et usumfructuando omnia suprscripta res; et per
                        singulo anno ex ipsis rebus reddere debeamus in <rs key="#Mother_churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs> Sancti Martini uno solido valentem <rs key="#Oil"
                            >oleo</rs>. Et si <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name
                                ref="Teudebertulus">Teupertulo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerico</rs> nepote nostro super nos vixerit caste
                        et servire voluerit eidem ecclesiae et ad honorem presbiterii pertingere
                        potuerit, cum voluntate <rs key="#Bishops">pontifici</rs> suprascripte
                        ecclesie licentiam habeat habitare in casa ipsius ecclesiae, serviendo in
                        omibus officiis bonis. <foreign>Si riservano inoltre</foreign> de rebus
                        mobilibus et de usumfructum in nostra sit potestate pro anime nostrae
                        remedium despensandi (…). Actum in <placeName key="#Vici"><rs
                                key="#Vici #Churches">vico</rs> Valeriana</placeName>, ad <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam </rs><orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/618">Sancti Fridiani</orgName>.
                            <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: + Aliperti offerturi; (ss) Rodpert
                        presbitero; (ss) <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name ref="Deusdona"
                                >Deusdona</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>; (ss) <persName key="#Witness #Priests"
                                ><name ref="Stabilis">Stabilis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>; (ss) <persName key="#Witness #Priests"
                                ><name ref="Sassus">Saxo</name></persName> indignus <rs
                            key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>; (ss) <persName key="#Witness #Subdeacons"
                                ><name ref="Desudedit">Desudedit</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconus</rs>; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Agibrandus"
                            >Agiprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName
                            key="#Writer #Deacons"><name ref="Osprandus">Osprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
